{"tid":1130324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登搞搞票好有公信力？","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T03:51:41.000Z","uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c347db441176edc60d4d23e0bcc48ab6ef91e75","tid":1130324,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"大家都只係1個account,  讀過幾個course最多都係2, 3個。<br />\n<br />\n連登搞投票本身就真係反映到社會實際支持嘅人數。<br />\n<br />\n如果最好就攞埋身份證尾3 個數字，或要求各院校洽一洽個學生number,  <br />\n 確保每人一個account。<br />\n<br />\n將來連登個投票會好有社會公信力。"},{"pid":"7c91e32cb57cd03f2944d02d9de52e8602e55d5c","tid":1130324,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"想搞監控呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無端端攞咩資料"},{"pid":"54f02359784108d347a71878200321430b5c0e96","tid":1130324,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"搞搞震就得"},{"pid":"9425eeccc9f44dc5bf411a7ea8dcf602d72d17d2","tid":1130324,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"就算唔攞， 有時d投票本身都比discuss有公信力啦。"},{"pid":"0357b7cda2850cbf8bb6db21fb204080353e9a48","tid":1130324,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"但好似冇呢個功能？<br />\n<br />\n例如囚犯轉送遊行。<br />\n<br />\n開3個選項出來：<br />\n<br />\n支持， 會遊行(日期， 地點)<br />\n支持，(其他support)<br />\n支持， 不遊行<br />\n不支持， 咁已經知道社會個風氣先。"},{"pid":"7b46821762ac4167fff5d30de74db71557456405","tid":1130324,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"你講d瘋嘅野， 警察會trace唔到你  咩？"},{"pid":"1925e924d48a7065f63d5c8e4434cf1ff8da5776","tid":1130324,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"轉軚快過火箭、炒車當食飯嘅連登仔有乜公信力？"}]}